{
  "stem": "16571.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't realize at the time that people were-- people were starving of hunger.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "People were being shot and killed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know what I would have done if I'd have known.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were working like Sunday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Sunday was a day off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Sunday afternoon.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They work six and a half days a week.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Sunday afternoon was off.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we used to go like people go today to Hyde Park for a walk round up and down on the-- on the Appellplatz.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "People used to go and nobody bothered you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was like a party more or less, Sunday afternoon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It wasn't, of course, a party.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But they work six and a half days a week.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That's how it was in Buchenwald when I was there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In fact, I was talking to a friend of mine, Morris Friedman.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we worked it out the day they came and called my name how to take me off to another camp, he more or less took my bed.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we sort of talked about it years later.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we worked it out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He says, I probably got your bed, the way I was describing it, next to the window, da da da, and so on and so on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were three bunks, and there was two people-- two people to a bed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was-- there was not as like in-- in-- what can I say.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Buchenwald, at the bottom part where there was these big blocks from 60 up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was bunk beds which we used to take four people at a time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was about 12 or 16, four-- four high.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in-- once they sort of-- you went there for a sorting out, I would call it.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
